			</div>
	    	<div class="col-xs-11 col-md-3 services-mobile-padding">
	    		<h4>Hotels</h4>
	    		<p>We are the exclusive child care provider of choice for a number of prestigious hotels across London. Our team are straight to work with a number of activities and London adventures to make sure your child’s stay is just as enjoyable as your own.</p>
	    	</div>
	    	<div class="col-xs-1 col-sm-1 col-md-1">
		    	<div class="our-services-icon larger-icon">
					<i class="fa fa-plane"></i>
				</div>
			</div>
	    	<div class="col-xs-11 col-md-3 services-mobile-padding">
